# PETN 16240 single-frame comparison
units real
atom_style charge
read_data data.reax
replicate 7 8 5
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
pair_style reaxff NULL
pair_coeff * * ffield.reax C H O N
fix qeq all qeq/reaxff 1 0.0 10.0 1.0e-6 reaxff maxiter 1000
thermo 1
thermo_style custom step temp pe press pxx pyy pzz pxy pxz pyz etotal
dump frc all custom 1 forces.dump id fx fy fz
dump chg all custom 1 charges.dump id q
run 0
